    <item>
      <title>米塔尔：债券投资平台催生金融衍生品需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/mittal-bond-investment-platforms-build-demand-for-fi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[IndiaBonds 联合创始人兼董事 Aditi Mittal 表示，通过在线债券平台提供商，国内散户参与度的不断提高正在推动对固定收益的需求。她在“彭博市场：亚洲”节目中与 Paul Allen 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/mittal-bond-investment-platforms-build-demand-for-fi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:53:52 GMT</pubDate>
